510
00:24:16.230 --> 00:24:18.760
That Kitetsu looks different now.

511
00:24:20.050 --> 00:24:23.150
It seems to have found a good owner.

512
00:24:24.270 --> 00:24:28.530
That Kitetsu III of yours is my craft.

513
00:24:28.940 --> 00:24:30.330
Really?!

514
00:24:31.020 --> 00:24:32.200
Boy.

515
00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:37.610
Lady Hiyori gifted Enma to you, which I would wager
feels oddly comfortable in your hand, correct?

516
00:24:38.760 --> 00:24:41.040
It is the same as any cursed sword.

517
00:24:41.550 --> 00:24:44.310
The weak cannot handle them.

518
00:24:44.310 --> 00:24:48.930
But the main reason it fits so comfortably
in your hand is, by some twist of fate...

519
00:24:49.350 --> 00:24:54.060
because Wado Ichimonji and Enma
were crafted by the same person!

520
00:24:55.900 --> 00:24:59.580
The master swordsmith Shimotsuki Kozaburo.

521
00:24:59.580 --> 00:25:05.030
That man illegally emigrated
from Wano more than fifty years ago.

522
00:25:05.560 --> 00:25:11.340
Perhaps Lady Hiyori gave you the memento from
her father because she recognized that sword.

523
00:25:13.950 --> 00:25:17.080
Enma has not yet been forged
into a black blade!

524
00:25:17.780 --> 00:25:20.960
Its rank can be raised depending on you.

525
00:25:22.620 --> 00:25:24.830
Then that's just what I'll do!

526
00:25:27.020 --> 00:25:28.770
Udon is secure?!

527
00:25:28.770 --> 00:25:30.740
Yes, sir. No problems here.

528
00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:32.640
Huh, I must have been misinformed!

529
00:25:33.000 --> 00:25:37.110
Yes, sir. Nothing has changed here in Udon.

530
00:25:37.110 --> 00:25:40.440
We continue to guard the prisoners.

531
00:25:40.710 --> 00:25:41.610
Over and out.

532
00:25:42.630 --> 00:25:45.840
I don't trust him acting so strange!

533
00:25:46.490 --> 00:25:51.070
But as long as I have this information,
it's more than enough.

534
00:25:46.860 --> 00:25:51.070
Moved from Habu Port to Tokage Port.
Kozuki Hiyori Lives
Northern Region

535
00:25:51.670 --> 00:25:59.570
"Moved from Habu Port to Tokage Port.
Kozuki Hiyori lives. Northern Region," huh?

536
00:26:40.970 --> 00:26:43.160
Watch out, Kaido!

537
00:26:45.770 --> 00:26:48.250
Gather 'round!

538
00:26:49.320 --> 00:26:52.840
Fair weather graces the Flower Capital
as the cherry blossoms fall.

539
00:26:53.780 --> 00:26:56.010
The day of the Fire Festival has arrived!

540
00:26:56.780 --> 00:27:03.440
Meanwhile, in the shadows looms a battle
that would sway even the fate of the world!

